high_descs: Turn left and walk to the table.
Grab the knife from the table.
Turn right and walk, then turn right again to face the counter left of the sink.
Slice the potato on the counter.
Turn around and walk then turn left and face the table.
Place the knife on the table.
Turn left and walk straight then turn right and face the counter next to the sink.
Grab a potato slice from the counter.
Turn left then right and face the microwave above the stove.
Heat the potato slice in the microwave for 1 second.
Turn around and walk then turn left to face the table.
Place the slice on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a warmed potato slice on the table.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the white table
Pick up the knife that is on the table
Cross the room towards the sink
Slice the bread that is over the counter, on the left side of the sink
Cross the room and go to the dark round dining table
Put the knife on the table
Go back to the counter where you sliced the bread
Pick up a slice of bread
Turn left towards the kitchen range and stand facing the microwave
Put the bread slice in the microwave and heat it.
Take the bread slice to the round dining table
Drop the slice on the table
anns.task_desc: Put a warm slice of bread on the dining table

high_descs: Turn left and go to the white table in front.
Pick up the yellow knife on the table.
Turn around and go to the counter on the left of the sink.
Slice the potato on the counter.
Turn around and go to the gray table in the left corner.
Place the yellow knife on the top of the table.
Turn left and go back to the counter on the left of the sink.
Pick up one slice of the potato from the counter.
Move over left to the front of the microwave above the stove.
Remove the potato slice after heating it in the microwave.
Turn around and go back to the gray table in the left corner.
Place the potato slice on the table on the right.
anns.task_desc: Put the heated slice of potato on the table.
